[02/08/2017 13:04:21] <font color="#00ff00">así.</font>
[02/08/2017 13:04:23] <font color="#00ff00">(LEE) "Dan Wilson, Birch.</font>
[02/08/2017 13:04:25] <font color="#00ff00">Si desea usted vender su tierra</font>
