[02/08/2017 23:04:50] <font color="#ffffff">-¿Yo degenerado?</font>
[02/08/2017 23:04:52] <font color="#ffffff">Sujétame las gafas.</font>
[02/08/2017 23:04:55] <font color="#00ff00">¡Ah!</font>
[02/08/2017 23:04:55] <font color="#ffffff">(GRITAN)</font>
[02/08/2017 23:05:04] <font color="#ffff00">Hola.</font>
